article.description: — Jeenathan Williams had 19 points and Maceo Jack registered 18 points as Buffalo rolled past Rider 87-65 on Saturday.
article.headline: Jack scores 18 to carry Buffalo past Rider 87-65
article.linkText: Jack scores 18 to carry Buffalo past Rider 87-65
article.story: BUFFALO, N.Y. -- — Jeenathan Williams had 19 points and Maceo Jack registered 18 points as Buffalo rolled past Rider 87-65 on Saturday. Keishawn Brewton added 12 points and Josh Mballa had seven rebounds for Buffalo (2-1). Corey McKeithan had 13 points for the Broncs (2-3). Dwight Murray Jr. and Allen Powell each had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
